import React, { useState } from 'react';
import "@radix-ui/themes/styles.css";
import { Table, Box, Button, Flex } from '@radix-ui/themes';
import ActionMenu from './DropdownMenu';
import { useQuery } from '@tanstack/react-query';
import { getUsers } from '../until/api';

const UserTable: React.FC<any> = () => { 

    const [currentPage, setCurrentPage] = useState(1);
    const [searchText, setSearchText] = useState("");

    const { userData, status } = useQuery({
        queryKey: ["users", currentPage, searchText],
        queryFn: () => getUsers({ currentPage, searchText }),
    });


    console.log("data", userData)

    return (
        <Box>
            <Table.Root>
                <Table.Header>
                    <Table.ColumnHeaderCell>User</Table.ColumnHeaderCell>
                    <Table.ColumnHeaderCell>Role</Table.ColumnHeaderCell>
                    <Table.ColumnHeaderCell>Joined</Table.ColumnHeaderCell>
                    <Table.ColumnHeaderCell></Table.ColumnHeaderCell>
                </Table.Header>
            
                <Table.Body>
                    {userData.map((userData) => (
                        <Table.Row>
                        <Table.RowHeaderCell>Danilo Sousa</Table.RowHeaderCell>
                        <Table.Cell>danilo@example.com</Table.Cell>
                        <Table.Cell>Developer</Table.Cell>
                        <Table.Cell>
                            <ActionMenu user="" />
                        </Table.Cell>
                    </Table.Row>
                    ))} 
                    <Table.Row>
                        <Table.RowHeaderCell>Danilo Sousa</Table.RowHeaderCell>
                        <Table.Cell>danilo@example.com</Table.Cell>
                        <Table.Cell>Developer</Table.Cell>
                        <Table.Cell>
                            <ActionMenu user="" />
                        </Table.Cell>
                    </Table.Row>

                    <Table.Row>
                        <Table.RowHeaderCell>Zahra Ambessa</Table.RowHeaderCell>
                        <Table.Cell>zahra@example.com</Table.Cell>
                        <Table.Cell>Admin</Table.Cell>
                        <Table.Cell>
                            <ActionMenu user="" />
                        </Table.Cell>
                    </Table.Row>

                    <Table.Row>
                        <Table.RowHeaderCell>Jasper Eriksson</Table.RowHeaderCell>
                        <Table.Cell>jasper@example.com</Table.Cell>
                        <Table.Cell>Developer</Table.Cell>
                        <Table.Cell>
                            <ActionMenu user="" />
                        </Table.Cell>
                    </Table.Row>
                </Table.Body>

                <Flex justify="end" align="end" gap="2">
                    <Button disabled={currentPage == 1 ? true : false}>
                        Previous
                    </Button>
                    <Button>
                        Next
                    </Button>
                </Flex>
            </Table.Root> 
        </Box> 
    )


}

export default UserTable;
